Acknowledgments
===============

This project uses the following third-party libraries:

- Servo: Arduino library for controlling servo motors
  - Author: Arduino
  - License: LGPL-2.1
  - Repository: https://github.com/arduino-libraries/Servo

- Wire: Arduino library for communication over I2C
  - Author: Arduino
  - License: LGPL-2.1
  - Repository: https://github.com/arduino/ArduinoCore-avr/tree/master/libraries/Wire

- Adafruit_GFX: Adafruit graphics library for display devices
  - Author: Adafruit Industries
  - License: BSD-3-Clause
  - Repository: https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit-GFX-Library

- Adafruit_SSD1306: Adafruit library for SSD1306 OLED displays
  - Author: Adafruit Industries
  - License: BSD-3-Clause
  - Repository: https://github.com/adafruit/Adafruit_SSD1306

- EncoderButton: Arduino library for handling rotary encoder button input
  - Author: Stutchbury
  - License: MIT
  - Repository: https://github.com/Stutchbury/EncoderButton

- RF24: Arduino library for nRF24L01(+) 2.4GHz Wireless Transceiver
  - Author: TMRh20
  - License: GPL-3.0
  - Repository: https://github.com/nRF24/RF24

- HCSR04: Arduino library for HC-SR04 ultrasonic distance sensor
  - Author: Martyn Currey
  - License: MIT
  - Repository: https://github.com/Martinsos/arduino-lib-hc-sr04
